The '''Star Winds Lounge''' was considered to be the swankiest nightclub on the ''[[Queen of Empire]]'' in [[1 BBY/Legends|1 BBY]]. [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] once went there and met [[Bria Tharen]] onboard.

